Description: GSAuto is a fast and scalable R package for processing Illumina Infinium methylation beadchip IDAT files 
    (27k, 450k, 850k/EPIC v1.0, 935k/EPIC v2.0, MSA). It extracts probe intensities, computes beta values, detection P-values, 
    and detection rates, with superior efficiency compared to Illumina GenomeStudio, supporting cross-platform workflows.
